{"tid":1141374,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"特意在五姊妹生日這天公佈六喜臨門，《五等分的花嫁》動畫第2期製作決定","createTime":"2019-05-06T12:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T01:48:02.000Z","uid":75050,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cd2cf04a92ee7a7a490d2d3105d3051ce3ef60a4","tid":1141374,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:28:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/85777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F85777&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHhR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=2d6f52fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/85777</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/00-22.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F00-22.jpg%3F&h=e6bd52f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<strong>特意在五姊妹生日這天公佈六喜臨門，《五等分的花嫁》動畫第2期製作決定</strong><br />\n作者: 填海紳士 日期: 05/05/2019<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/%E4%BA%94%E7%AD%89%E5%88%86%E7%9A%84%E8%8A%B1%E5%AB%81-2-1.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F%25E4%25BA%2594%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%25AB%2581-2-1.jpg%3F&h=ef6c22c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為早幾天已經從中國網絡那邊傳出了偷跑情報<br />\n<br />\n所以對於不少關注《五等分的花嫁》的粉絲來說，這其實已經不算是新聞了<br />\n<br />\n不過這種重大宣佈還是以官方公開為準：《五等分的花嫁》動畫第2期製作決定！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/5Hanayome_anime/status/1125001006750658561/photo/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F5Hanayome_anime%2Fstatus%2F1125001006750658561%2Fphoto%2F1&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHhR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=ab735af0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F5Hanayome_anime%2Fstatus%2F1125001006750658561%2Fphoto%2F1&h=e87333ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/5Hanayome_anime/status/1125001006750658561/photo/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wa6xbjVYuEo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWa6xbjVYuEo&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHhR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=8faf6f22\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wa6xbjVYuEo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/%E4%BA%94%E7%AD%89%E5%88%86%E7%9A%84%E8%8A%B1%E5%AB%81-2.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F%25E4%25BA%2594%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%25AB%2581-2.jpg%3F&h=47ca762e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/5Hanayome/status/1124960762257002496/photo/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F5Hanayome%2Fstatus%2F1124960762257002496%2Fphoto%2F1&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHhR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=cb08d4bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F5Hanayome%2Fstatus%2F1124960762257002496%2Fphoto%2F1&h=a257b0f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/5Hanayome/status/1124960762257002496/photo/1</a><br />\n<br />\n官方選在5月5日這天發表動畫第2期消息當然有其用意，因為5月5日就是中野家五姊妹的生日<br />\n<br />\n官方也特意選在5月5日舉辨《五等分的花嫁》的線下活動，並在活動的晚上場次以短片形式向觀眾正式宣佈這個好消息<br />\n<br />\n而且這場活動的BD會在9月25日發售，定價9800日元<br />\n<br />\n五姊妹生日加上動畫第2期消息六喜臨門，各路英雄好漢同喜同喜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-13.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F01-13.jpg%3F&h=8154b1d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-10.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F02-10.jpg%3F&h=cf475fed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>幾乎全是男生的活動人龍</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>另外一提在《五等分的花嫁》官網首頁還有五姊妹的生日語音收聽</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.tbs.co.jp/anime/5hanayome/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tbs.co.jp%2Fanime%2F5hanayome%2F&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHhR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=08444516\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.tbs.co.jp/anime/5hanayome/</a>"},{"pid":"c7dfdd2142af553db86b2a727d749b3f9aa147db","tid":1141374,"uid":75050,"like":36,"dislike":10,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K8CJpbB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK8CJpbB.jpg&h=9a3b8bc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f47d4dce7d0f39a963cc8091d41f3f76b0b8c2a4","tid":1141374,"uid":198309,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c7dfdd2142af553db86b2a727d749b3f9aa147db","tid":1141374,"uid":75050,"like":36,"dislike":10,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K8CJpbB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK8CJpbB.jpg&h=9a3b8bc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafc5b987b0469ed2e17576a2fe944b90ebe096b","tid":1141374,"uid":105446,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"唔係話好崩咩仲出"},{"pid":"131ef38b7892e9db2b0055a401fb7a1d8770be80","tid":1141374,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dafc5b987b0469ed2e17576a2fe944b90ebe096b","tid":1141374,"uid":105446,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"唔係話好崩咩仲出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:37:46.000Z","msg":"知錯能改"},{"pid":"b89471eea327a083e2d0fbe9fa39509ff3e4f1e8","tid":1141374,"uid":14065,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"dafc5b987b0469ed2e17576a2fe944b90ebe096b","tid":1141374,"uid":105446,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"唔係話好崩咩仲出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:40